|image2    = Tutorial Dreamwalker (V) 2.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_609602.png>-<Tutorial Dreamwalker (V) 2.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
