|image3    = Tutorial Dreamwalker (V) 3.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_609603.png>-<Tutorial Dreamwalker (V) 3.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
|text3     = By {{Color|h|nobold=1|interacting}} with Control Panels, the Dream Module {{Color|h|nobold=1|can be moved along the designated trajectory}}. When moving the Dream Module, the scattered dream bubbles on its surface {{Color|h|nobold=1|will also move with it}}.
|image4    = Tutorial Dreamwalker (V) 4.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_609604.png>-<Tutorial Dreamwalker (V) 4.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
|text4     = When the placement of the scattered dream bubbles {{Color|h|nobold=1|meets the requirements of forming a Bubble Bridge}}, these dream bubbles will {{Color|h|nobold=1|congeal}}. When this happens, {{Color|h|nobold=1|approach with a Bubble Charge}} to manifest a Bubble Bridge.
